      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，标题就叫\"Browsing the online shop\"。我分成两个主要阶段：进入商城和浏览商品，这样结构清晰吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
